description:
The teaching of a secret rapture has gained popularity in the Christian world. This belief teaches that Jesus will come in secret and that those who are ready for Him will be “raptured” or caught up to Heaven, while the rest  remain alive on this earth for 1000 years with another opportunity to repent and accept Christ. Is the teaching Biblical, or is a great deception that will cause many to be eternally lost?
